OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police Interim
OL,4,CChief Constable to stay until 2027
OL,6,FThe interim Chief Constable of Devon
OL,7,Fand Cornwall Police has agreed to stay
OL,8,Fin the role for a further 16 months.
OL,10,FJames Vaughan was appointed in
OL,11,FDecember 2024, after the suspension of
OL,12,Fthe Acting Chief Constable Jim Colwell.
OL,14,FThe Police and Crime Commissioner,
OL,15,FAlison Hernandez, has extended Mr
OL,16,FVaughan's contract to 2027 and said
OL,17,Fpeople living in Devon, Cornwall and
OL,18,Fthe Isles of Scilly would benefit from
OL,19,Fa "much-needed period of stability."
