OL,6,FShe said: "I have been really pleased
OL,7,Fto see how Chief Constable Vaughan has
OL,8,Ftackled head-on several legacy issues
OL,9,Ffrom the period of unstable leadership
OL,10,Fthat preceded his appointment.
OL,12,F"It's so important that Mr Vaughan and
OL,13,FI take a unified approach in
OL,14,Fdelivering my Police and Crime Plan
OL,15,Fpriorities.
OL,17,FShe added: "I look forward to the
OL,18,Fcoming 16 months which I am confident
OL,19,Fwill see more good work and continued
OL,20,Fimprovement under Mr Vaughan's
OL,21,Fexperienced leadership."
