OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police Interim
OL,4,CChief Constable to stay until 2027
OL,6,FChief Constable James Vaughan said he
OL,7,Fhas "really enjoyed" leading the force
OL,8,Fover the past eight months.
OL,10,FHe said: "It is a personal privilege
OL,11,Fto be asked by the Commissioner to
OL,12,Fstay on in my role.
OL,14,F"I have really enjoyed leading this
OL,15,Ffantastic organisation and seeing the
OL,16,Fgreat work officers, staff and
OL,17,Fvolunteers do every day to keep our
OL,18,Fcommunities safe.
