OL,6,F"Despite some challenging times, we
OL,7,Fhave made considerable progress over
OL,8,Fthe last few years and that is
OL,9,Ftestament to the hard work of everyone
OL,10,Fin the force.."
OL,12,FMr Colwell has returned to his
OL,13,Fsubstantive role as Deputy Chief
OL,14,FConstable and has resumed his duties.
OL,16,FThe process to recruit a substantive
OL,17,FChief Constable is due to begin in the
OL,18,Fsummer of 2026.
